The paper deals with a deep learning architecture for image fusion, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves the design of fusion strategies, which could be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper may involve some information theory (cs.IT) in the encoding and reconstruction processes.
